Package gui_code

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BuyStuffWindow
    The window for purchasing goods/upgrades from an island's shop
    GameOver
    The window that appears at the end of the game
    IslandWindow
    The window to represent an island that the player is on
    MainMenu
    The Main Menu of the game Is essentially a title screen and a start button.
    PreGame
    The GUI window that gets the setup prompts from the player, those being Their Trader name Their Choice of Ship Their desired duration of days
    QuitWindow
    A simple quit window that asks if a user wants to quit the program.
    SailingEvent
    The window that displays and runs random events during a player's voyage
    SelectSail
    The window for choosing an island to sail to, as well as a route, and then setting sail.
    SellStuffWindow
    The window for selling goods to an island's shop
    ShipView
    The window for viewing the properties, cargo and sales of a ship
    UiManager
    The program that manages all the different windows and ensures they co-operate
    ViewIslands
    The window for looking at all islands currently in the game As well as their shops and routes
